lead_paragraph: Top Chinese woman golfer Shanshan Feng will compete at the Rio Games despite concerns over Zika virus and the world number 12 says she fears for the sport's Olympic future following some high-profile withdrawals from the men's competition.

headline.print_headline: Top China Golfer Feng Not to Allow Zika Fears Ruin Rio Dream
